Binary change: FreeImage.dll
================================

Purpose
-------
Replace Quivi's bundled FreeImage runtime with a WebP-capable x86 FreeImage
runtime so static .webp files can be detected and decoded through the existing
pyfreeimage loader.

Changed file
------------
FreeImage.dll

