Compatibility note
------------------
FreeImage 3.18.0 no longer exports the old _FreeImage_RotateClassic@12 symbol
that Quivi's bundled pyfreeimage wrapper tries to bind at startup. See
pyfreeimage-rotateclassic-binding.diff for the companion library.zip patch.

